sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor ChuToChuc as ChuToChuc
actor NguoiDung as NguoiDungMoi
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgSvc as OrganizationService
participant OrgDb as Mongo_Organization_Membership
participant RoleSync as RolePermissionService

Note over ChuToChuc,RoleSync: Chặng 1 - Tạo tổ chức và mời thành viên
ChuToChuc->>Client: Tạo tổ chức mới
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations
Gateway->>OrgSvc: Forward request
OrgSvc->>OrgDb: Tạo Organization + Membership(owner)
OrgSvc->>OrgDb: Seed phòng ban và kênh mặc định
OrgSvc->>RoleSync: Đồng bộ role mặc định
OrgSvc-->>Client: Trả về tổ chức đã tạo

ChuToChuc->>Client: Mời thành viên
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/members
Gateway->>OrgSvc: Forward request
OrgSvc->>OrgDb: Upsert membership pending
OrgSvc-->>Client: Kết quả mời
